# Announcing
Announcing an open source project is an important step that must be done correctly. It involves providing details about the project, including its goals, features, project name, description, key functionalities, and how developers can contribute. The project may attract attention, encourage developers to interact with the developer community, and foster collaboration by making a clear and simple announcement.
<br>
<br>
We must place the announcement pages on the project home page and make sure the announcement contains keywords that make our project easier for search engines to find in order to increase the announcement's usefulness.
